bschedules.com/ncaa-17/2017-hawaii-warriors-football-schedule.php|publisher=FB Schedules|accessdate=December 28, 2016}}</ref>\n\u2606Spectrum Sports Hawaii simulcast the UMass game. The game was available on Spectrum Sports Hawaii statewide and was not part of the teams PPV package.\n\n==Game summaries==\n===at UMass===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road='''Rainbow Warriors'''\n|R1=7|R2= 7|R3= 7|R4=17\n|Home=Minutemen\n|H1=7|H2= 7|H3= 14|H4=7\n}}\n{{see also|2017 UMass Minutemen football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n{{CollegeSecondaryHeader|team=Hawaii Rainbow Warriors|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|-\n| 2\u20130\n| 2017\n| HAW, 38\u201335\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===Western Carolina===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=Catamounts\n|R1=0 |R2=10 |R3=8 |R4=0\n|Home='''Rainbow Warriors'''\n|H1=7 |H2=14 |H3=13 |H4=7\n}}\n{{see also|2017 Western Carolina Catamounts football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Hawaii Rainbow Warriors|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| colspan=3| First meeting\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===at UCLA===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=Rainbow Warriors\n|R1=0 |R2=7 |R3=7 |R4=9\n|Home='''Bruins'''\n|H1=14 |H2=21 |H3=14 |H4=7\n}}\n{{see also|2017 UCLA Bruins football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n{{CollegeSecondaryHeader|team=Hawaii Rainbow Warriors|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|-\n| 0\u20132\n| 1939\n| UCLA, 32\u20137\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===at Wyoming===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=Rainbow Warriors\n|R1= 0|R2= 7|R3= 7|R4= 7|R5=0\n|Home='''Cowboys'''\n|H1= 0|H2= 7|H3= 7|H4= 7|H5=7\n}}\n{{see also|2017 Wyoming Cowboys football team|Hawaii\u2013Wyoming football rivalry}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n{{CollegeSecondaryHeader|team=Hawaii Rainbow Warriors|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|-\n| 9\u201313\n| 2014\n| HAW, 38\u201328\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===Colorado State===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Roa